00:09:08.520 --> 00:09:10.610
of taking students with disabilities

00:09:10.610 --> 00:09:15.260
that the mainstream school
classroom has decided

00:09:15.260 --> 00:09:19.350
don't fit there, and they send them to.

00:09:19.350 --> 00:09:21.180
They use public money and send them to

00:09:21.180 --> 00:09:23.163
these non public schools.

00:09:25.370 --> 00:09:30.370
We have found that
because they're segregated

00:09:32.010 --> 00:09:37.010
because many of the students
have limited verbal skills

00:09:37.700 --> 00:09:41.150
